---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Our Shopify Integration Is Available Now - parcelLab"
  description="The parcelLab Shopify integration enables businesses to quickly access the platform and create tailored post-purchase customer experiences."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Product</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Our Shopify Integration Is Available Now</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2021-01-15">January 15, 2021</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>3 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          The parcelLab platform's Shopify integration is here. Businesses can now quickly and easily access the parcelLab platform via Shopify, granting access to comprehensive order information that powers tailored post-purchase customer experiences.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">What Does the Shopify Integration Do?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The integration connects your Shopify store with the parcelLab platform, enabling you to leverage order data for creating personalized post-purchase communications. Once connected, you can:
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Design <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">end-to-end customer experiences</strong> from order confirmation to delivery</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Add <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">personalized content</strong> based on order history</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Include <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">product recommendations</strong> and review links</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Create <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">targeted messages</strong> aligned with business objectives</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Add <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">NPS scores</strong> to boost review collection</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Include <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">vouchers</strong> to drive repeat site visits</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Get Started in Minutes</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The integration has received positive feedback from early adopters. One customer completed the entire onboarding process during a brief 10-minute call, demonstrating just how straightforward the implementation is.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The solution is particularly valuable for online retailers who may not have dedicated development resources. The Shopify integration removes the technical barriers to adopting the parcelLab platform, making personalized post-purchase communications accessible to merchants of all sizes.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Quick Setup</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">One customer completed the entire onboarding process in just 10 minutes. No dedicated development resources required.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The Shopify integration streamlines platform access while enabling merchants to leverage customer order data for creating personalized post-purchase communications that drive measurable business outcomes. Integration documentation is available through parcelLab's developer portal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
